inated by some internal instability processes, rather than an\nimpact with an asteroidal body. Due to the peculiar characteristics of this\nevent, further observations and investigations are necessary in order to\nenlight the nature of the physical processes that determined it.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 6 Jan 2008 16:17:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
