equivalent age. Fitting a free amount of blue\nstars in addition to the SSP model to mimic the BHB improves and stabilizes the\nfit and restores ages in agreement with CMDs studies. This method is\npotentially able to disentangle age or BHB effects in extragalactic clusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 6 Jan 2008 16:18:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
