re appears to help to simply explain the appearance and the\nspectrum of supernova 1987A.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Jan 2008 08:32:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 19 Jul 2008 07:44:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-07-19"}
